title: Wildlife accidents increase in October and November
text:
Wildlife accidents increase in October and November 
This is the time of year when many animals become very active and their movements change dramatically. Many animals are trying to prepare for the cold winter months ahead, and some become more active because of daylight changes and breeding seasons.
